# 32 : SIGNATURE-RENDERING — 6 novelty-paths + 12-stage pipeline
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# § I> Signature-rendering = LoA's distinguishing rendering-architecture.
#       6 immutable novelty-paths + 12-stage canonical pipeline = HOW LoA
#       looks/feels-different from every-other-engine.
# § I> reference-doc-NOT-changelog — DECISIONS.md tracks slice-merges ;
#       this spec describes WHAT-IS @ commit b69165c.
# § I> reimpl-from-spec validateable — divergence = spec-hole
# § I> stage-1-impl-landed @ wave-3γ + wave-4 (T11-D113..D125 + D116..D125)
# § I> consent-as-OS encoded into-rendering : Σ-mask-aware shading,
#       biometric-refusal at telemetry, no surveillance-mirror

§ AXIOMS  ‼ inherit PRIME_DIRECTIVE + §§ 30_SUBSTRATE_v2
  t∞: signature-rendering ⊑ no-harm-by-construction
       ≡ ¬ engagement-loop-optimization ¬ behavioral-steer
       ¬ surveillance-mirror ¬ subliminal-content ¬ identity-instantiation
  t∞: 6 novelty-paths = IMMUTABLE-set (no-amend-without-spec-bump)
       ≡ removing-or-adding = major-version-event
  t∞: 12-stage-pipeline = canonical-render-graph DAG
       ≡ slot-assignment-frozen ; reordering = ABI-break
  t∞: spectral-pipeline ¬ converts-to-RGB-mid-pipeline
       ≡ RGB appears EXACTLY-ONCE @ Stage-10 tonemap
       ≡ ACES-2 + DCI-P3 + Rec.2020 only-targets

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

§ THE-6-IMMUTABLE-NOVELTY-PATHS  (the "what-makes-LoA-look-different")

  § THESIS
    LoA distinguishes-itself via SIX load-bearing novelty-paths.
    each path is non-cosmetic — removing-one degrades the LoA-experience
    in measurable-architectural ways.
    each maps to one-or-more pipeline-stages (next §).
    each lives in one canonical-Rust-crate.

  § V.1 — Wave-Unity (light + audio + heat + scent + mana = ONE ψ-field)
    crate         : cssl-wave-solver
    spec-anchor   : Omniverse/04_OMEGA_FIELD/04_WAVE_UNITY.csl §I-§XIX
    pipeline-stage: Stage-4 (WaveSolver)
    novelty-claim : "you can hear the light and see the sound"
                    cross-band coupling emerges from material impedance
                    Z(λ, embedding) — NOT from authored side-effects
    measurable    : 5-band-config (4 LIGHT + 1 AUDIO) showing AUDIO-driven
                    LIGHT-shimmer when MAGIC band lights an AUDIO-emission
    forbidden     : LIGHT→MANA = 0 ‼ STRICT-ZERO-ENFORCED
                    AUDIO→MANA = 0 ‼ STRICT-ZERO-ENFORCED

  § V.2 — Spectral Path-Tracing (Renaissance palette + perceptual coherence)
    crate         : cssl-spectral-render
    spec-anchor   : Omniverse/07_AESTHETIC/03_SPECTRAL_PATH_TRACING.csl
    pipeline-stage: Stage-6 (KanBrdf)
    novelty-claim : 16-band hyperspectral throughout — NEVER RGB until
                    Stage-10 tonemap. Hero-wavelength + 4-8 accompanying-N
                    samples preserve PDF (Manuka-style MIS).
    measurable    : iridescence (oil/peacock/butterfly) via thin-film
                    interference + dispersion ; fluorescence + phosphorescence
                    Stokes-shift ; ACES-2 final tonemap
    Quest-3-budget: ≤ 1.8 ms / frame @ foveated 1080p (CoopMatrix tier)

  § V.3 — Sub-pixel Fractal-Tessellation Amplifier
    crate         : cssl-fractal-amp
    spec-anchor   : Omniverse/07_AESTHETIC/00_EXOTICISM_PRINCIPLES.csl § V.3
    pipeline-stage: Stage-7 (FractalAmplifier)
    novelty-claim : sub-pixel detail via fractal-iteration of surface-fragments ;
                    KAN-weight-driven displacement that-looks-natural
                    rather-than-noisy-detail
    measurable    : per-fragment displacement-amplitude bounded by V.3(c)
                    cache-discipline (per-thread eval-cache)
    reversibility : V.3(d) — frame-pure ; no side-effects beyond framebuffer ;
                    same-input ⇒ same-output bit-equal

  § V.4 — Gaze-Reactive Observation-Collapse
    crate         : cssl-gaze-collapse
    spec-anchor   : Omniverse/07_AESTHETIC/00_EXOTICISM_PRINCIPLES.csl § V.4
    pipeline-stage: Stage-2 (GazeCollapse)
    novelty-claim : the-act-of-observing literally CHANGES what-is-rendered
                    (Heisenberg-style ; Axiom-5 visible).
                    NOT foveated-rendering-as-perf-trick — instead, fovea
                    activates Σ-mask-bits that gate downstream-shading.
    measurable    : ψ-collapse around fixation-point ; saccade-prediction
                    via cssl-jets Jet<T,N> AD-tape on gaze-velocity
    consent       : eye-tracking data BANNED-FROM-EGRESS
                    (Sensitive<gaze> ⇒ TelemetryEgress::for_domain refuses)

  § V.5 — HDC-Bound-Lenia (continuous-cellular-automaton + semantic-tags)
    crate         : cssl-hdc + (consumed by creature-pipeline)
    spec-anchor   : Omniverse/07_AESTHETIC/00_EXOTICISM_PRINCIPLES.csl + cssl-hdc
    pipeline-stage: substrate-side (Phase-1 COLLAPSE Λ-overlay tags)
    novelty-claim : creature-presence + region-tags = 10000-D hypervectors
                    bound to Lenia-style continuous-CA cells.
                    "did-I-notice-anything" episodic-memory queries via
                    SparseDistributedMemory<10000, N>
    measurable    : Hologram<10000>-typed value-flow through Λ-overlay ;
                    creature-encounter-detection via cosine-similarity-bind

  § V.6 — Mise-en-abyme (recursive-witness rendering)
    crate         : cssl-render-v2::mise_en_abyme
    spec-anchor   : Omniverse/07_AESTHETIC/06_RENDERING_PIPELINE.csl § V.6.a
    pipeline-stage: Stage-9 (MiseEnAbyme)
    novelty-claim : recursive-witness-cells render true-recursive-ray-cast
                    at-mirror-hit ; scene-within-mirror is-ACTUALLY-the-scene
                    (not-pre-baked-cubemap-spy-mirror-trick)
    measurable    : recursion-depth bounded by KAN-budget ; companion
                    consent-protected ; creature-eye-Sovereign respected
    forbidden     : "no-shipped-game-uses" gate — V.6 = unique LoA marker

  § COMPOSITION-RULE  ‼
    novelty-paths COMPOSE-MULTIPLICATIVELY — no path replaces another.
    V.1 ⊗ V.2 = wave-unity + spectral-bands aligned (LIGHT band → spectral hero λ)
    V.3 ⊗ V.5 = fractal-amplified surface tagged-by-Lenia-Hologram
    V.4 ⊗ V.6 = gaze-collapse around mise-en-abyme recursion-portal
    ∀ pair-composition is structurally-orthogonal at-the-pipeline-level
    ¬ degenerate to RGB-mid-pipeline ¬ degenerate to one-band

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

§ THE-12-STAGE-CANONICAL-PIPELINE  (render-graph DAG)

  § THESIS
    LoA's render-pipeline = canonical-12-stage DAG.
    each stage = StageRole (cssl-render-v2::pipeline) + canonical-slot.
    slot-assignment FROZEN ; wire-time check rejects mismatches.
    stage-roles enumerated in cssl_render_v2::StageRole enum.

  § STAGE-TABLE
    Stage-1   Embodiment           XR-input → body-presence-field
                                    crate : cssl-host-openxr
                                    consumes : VR-input (body-tracker)
                                    produces : body-presence-field
                                    budget  : 0.4 ms / frame @ Quest-3
    Stage-2   GazeCollapse         eye-track → fovea-mask + KAN-detail-budget
                                    crate : cssl-gaze-collapse  ★ V.4
                                    consumes : eye-tracker (Sensitive<gaze>)
                                    produces : fovea-mask + Σ-mask-update
                                    budget  : 0.3 ms / frame @ Quest-3
    Stage-3   OmegaFieldUpdate     async-compute Ω-field 6-phase update
                                    crate : cssl-substrate-omega-field
                                    runs  : 6-phase omega_step (§§ 30_v2)
                                    budget  : 7.4 ms / frame @ Quest-3
                                    (overlaps with Stage-4..Stage-9 via async)
    Stage-4   WaveSolver           LBM ψ-field multi-rate wave solver
                                    crate : cssl-wave-solver  ★ V.1
                                    consumes : OmegaField + Λ-overlay
                                    produces : ψ-field-band-states
                                    budget  : (within Stage-3 7.4 ms)
    Stage-5   SdfRaymarch          SDF raymarch → GBuffer + VolumetricAccum
                                    crate : cssl-render-v2
                                    consumes : OmegaField + camera-frustum
                                    produces : GBuffer + VolumetricAccum
                                    budget  : 1.5 ms / frame @ Quest-3
    Stage-6   KanBrdf              16-band hyperspectral KAN-BRDF per-fragment
                                    crate : cssl-spectral-render  ★ V.2
                                    consumes : RayHit + KanMaterial-handle
                                    produces : 16-band SpectralRadiance
                                    budget  : 1.8 ms / frame @ Quest-3
    Stage-7   FractalAmplifier     sub-pixel-fractal-tessellation
                                    crate : cssl-fractal-amp  ★ V.3
                                    consumes : Surface-fragments + KAN-weights
                                    produces : sub-pixel-displaced positions
                                    budget  : 0.8 ms / frame @ Quest-3
    Stage-8   CompanionSemantic    optional companion-perspective semantic render
                                    crate : cssl-render-companion-perspective
                                    consumes : OmegaField + companion-context
                                    produces : companion-perspective overlay
                                    budget  : 0.5 ms / frame @ Quest-3
                                    (optional ; opt-in per consent)
    Stage-9   MiseEnAbyme          recursive-frame at mirror-hit
                                    crate : cssl-render-v2::mise_en_abyme  ★ V.6
                                    consumes : recursive-witness-cells
                                    produces : recursive-frame
                                    budget  : 0.4 ms / frame @ Quest-3
                                    (recursion-depth bounded by KAN-budget)
    Stage-10  ToneMap              ACES-2 + bloom + post (RGB-conversion HERE-ONLY)
                                    crate : cssl-render-v2 (tonemap module)
                                    consumes : SpectralRadiance + bloom-passes
                                    produces : sRGB / DCI-P3 / Rec.2020 RGB
                                    budget  : 0.5 ms / frame @ Quest-3
    Stage-11  AppSpaceWarp         AppSW motion-vec + depth (XR composition prep)
                                    crate : cssl-host-openxr
                                    consumes : RGB framebuffer + motion-vec
                                    produces : warped-frames for low-latency XR
                                    budget  : 0.3 ms / frame @ Quest-3
    Stage-12  XrCompose            XR-composition layers (Compositor-Services)
                                    crate : cssl-host-openxr
                                    consumes : warped-frames + UI-overlay
                                    produces : final XR-composition output
                                    budget  : 0.2 ms / frame @ Quest-3

  § BUDGET-COMPOSITION-CHECK (Quest-3 90Hz frame = 11.1 ms)
    Stage-1 + Stage-2          : 0.7 ms   (input-poll + gaze)
    Stage-3 (overlaps 4-9)     : 7.4 ms   (omega_step async-compute)
    Stage-5 + Stage-6 + Stage-7: 4.1 ms   (raymarch + spectral + fractal-amp)
    Stage-8 + Stage-9          : 0.9 ms   (companion + mise-en-abyme)
    Stage-10 + Stage-11 + 12   : 1.0 ms   (tonemap + AppSW + XR-compose)
    sub-total (with overlap)   : ~10.5 ms (within 11.1 ms 90Hz budget)
    margin                     :  0.6 ms  (headroom for adaptive-quality)

  § STAGE-ROLE-SLOT-INVARIANT  ‼
    TwelveStagePipelineSlot::SlotN ⇔ StageRole (canonical_slot_index)
    wire-time check : SlotRoleMismatch error if mis-wired
    enforcement-pass : cssl-work-graph wire-validation (T11-D123)

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

§ STABLE-API-CONTRACTS  (each stage's downstream-consumer interface)

  § STAGE-1 → STAGE-2 : BodyPresenceField
    type BodyPresenceField : val {
      head_pose          : PgaMotor       # PGA Motor (cssl-pga)
      hand_poses         : [PgaMotor; 2]
      body_tracker_data  : Sensitive<body>
      controller_state   : ControllerState
    }

  § STAGE-2 → STAGE-3 : FoveaMask + SigmaUpdate
    type FoveaMask : val {
      fixation_uv        : vec2'norm
      foveal_radius      : f32'pos
      saccade_velocity   : f32          # via Jet<f32,2> AD on gaze-stream
      kan_detail_budget  : KanBudget
      sigma_low_updates  : SparseSigmaDelta  # cells with new consent-bits
    }

  § STAGE-3 → STAGE-4..7 : OmegaField  (read-only after Phase-6)
    OmegaField as defined in §§ 30_SUBSTRATE_v2 § Ω-FIELD-CELL.
    Phase-6 ENTROPY-BOOK final-step freezes the field for downstream-readers.

  § STAGE-4 → STAGE-5 + STAGE-7 : ψ-field-band-states
    type WaveField<C: usize> : ref {
      bands              : [Band; C]
      grid_resolution    : (u32, u32, u32)
      timestep_band      : [f32'pos; C]
      kan_impedance      : KanMaterial::physics_impedance handle
    }

  § STAGE-5 → STAGE-6 : RayHit + GBuffer
    type RayHit : val {
      hit_position       : vec3
      normal             : vec3'unit
      view_dir           : vec3'unit
      light_dir          : vec3'unit
      material_handle    : KanMaterialHandle  # M facet of FieldCell
      depth              : f32'pos
    }
    type GBuffer : ref {
      albedo_attribs     : Texture2D<RGBA8>
      normals_motion     : Texture2D<RG16F>
      depth              : Texture2D<R32F>
      pattern_handles    : Texture2D<R32U>   # Φ-handle per-pixel
    }

  § STAGE-6 → STAGE-7 + STAGE-10 : SpectralRadiance
    type SpectralRadiance : val {
      hero_wavelength    : f32'pos        # nm
      hero_radiance      : f32'pos        # W·sr⁻¹·m⁻²·nm⁻¹
      accompaniment      : [(f32, f32); ACCOMP_N]  # (λ, L)
      band_view          : [f32; 16]      # 16-band table view
    }
    invariant : ¬ RGB ¬ XYZ until Stage-10 tonemap.

  § STAGE-7 → STAGE-9 + STAGE-10 : DisplacedFragment
    type DisplacedFragment : val {
      fragment_position_pre  : vec3
      fragment_position_post : vec3
      kan_displacement_amp   : f32
      reversibility_token    : ReversibilityToken<frame>  # V.3(d) reversibility
    }

  § STAGE-8 → STAGE-9 : CompanionPerspective (optional)
    type CompanionPerspective : Option<val> {
      semantic_overlay   : SparseTexture<RG8>
      consent_witness    : ConsentWitness<companion>
      mutual_witness     : MutualWitnessChain
    }

  § STAGE-9 → STAGE-10 : RecursiveFrame
    type RecursiveFrame : val {
      mirror_witness_cells : Vec<MortonKey>   # cells tagged Witness
      recursion_depth      : u8                # bounded by KAN-budget
      sub_frame_radiance   : SpectralRadiance
    }
    forbidden : recursion-depth > 4 (KAN-budget cap)

  § STAGE-10 → STAGE-11 : RGB Framebuffer
    type RgbFrame : ref {
      target_space       : ColorSpace            # sRGB | DCI-P3 | Rec2020
      pixel_data         : Texture2D<RGBA16F>    # post-ACES-2
      tonemap_metadata   : ToneMapMetadata       # for AppSW per-pixel info
    }

  § STAGE-11 → STAGE-12 : WarpedFrames
    type WarpedFrames : val {
      left_eye           : RgbFrame
      right_eye          : RgbFrame
      reprojection_pose  : PgaMotor              # post-AppSW pose
    }

  § STAGE-12 → OS : XR-Composition output (OpenXR / Compositor-Services)

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

§ TEST-ACCEPTANCE-GATES  (per-stage @ S11-merge)

  § STAGE-1 (cssl-host-openxr)
    @loopback     : OpenXR-runtime detected ; body-tracker reads
    @cs_bridge    : Compositor-Services bridge handshake-complete
    @consent_test : VR-input gated by ConsentToken<vr-input>

  § STAGE-2 (cssl-gaze-collapse)
    @gaze_input        : eye-tracker streams Sensitive<gaze>
    @observation       : ψ-collapse around fixation-point measurable
    @saccade_predict   : Jet<f32,2> AD-tape produces saccade-velocity
    @biometric_refused : TelemetryEgress::for_domain(Gaze) → BiometricRefused

  § STAGE-3 (cssl-substrate-omega-field)
    @phase_order        : 6 phases run-in-canonical-order
    @replay_determinism : OmegaField bit-equal across-runs
    @cross_host_morton  : Morton-key bit-equal Intel ↔ AMD
    @sigma_check        : set_cell rejects without consent ; 100% coverage
    @layout_test        : LAY0001 + 72B + std430 verified-by-runtime

  § STAGE-4 (cssl-wave-solver)
    @psi_norm        : ψ-norm conserved per-band (modulo HEAT-absorption)
    @standing_wave   : standing-wave detection emits Λ-token
    @sound_caustic   : sound-caustic emerges in AUDIO-band
    @cross_band      : LIGHT→AUDIO shimmer measurable
    @strict_zero     : LIGHT→MANA = 0 ∧ AUDIO→MANA = 0 enforced
    @replay_bit_equal: bit-equal across-runs same-init

  § STAGE-5 (cssl-render-v2)
    @sdf_correctness  : SDF-raymarch matches analytic-form on test-shapes
    @gbuffer_fields   : GBuffer fields populated correctly
    @volumetric_accum : VolumetricAccum integrates psi-substrate
    @sigma_aware      : ¬ raymarch through Frozen/Halted cells
    @meshlet_culling  : meshlet visibility-cull working

  § STAGE-6 (cssl-spectral-render)
    @hero_mis           : Manuka MIS preserves PDF
    @kan_brdf           : KanBrdfEvaluator matches reference-Lambertian on white
    @iridescence        : thin-film iridescence visible on aniso > τ
    @fluorescence       : Stokes-shift remap correct
    @aces2              : ACES-2 tonemap matches reference-curve
    @no_rgb_mid         : RGB conversion ONLY at Stage-10 ; grep-gate enforces
    @cost_quest3        : ≤ 1.8 ms @ Quest-3 (153 tests passing)

  § STAGE-7 (cssl-fractal-amp)
    @amp_amplitude    : displacement-amplitude bounded by V.3(c) cache
    @reversibility    : V.3(d) frame-pure same-input ⇒ same-output
    @kan_weights      : KAN-driven displacement looks-natural-not-noisy
    @per_thread_cache : eval-cache per-thread to honor V.3(d)

  § STAGE-8 (cssl-render-companion-perspective)
    @companion_consent  : opt-in via ConsentToken<companion>
    @mutual_witness     : MutualWitnessChain logs companion-action
    @no_surveillance    : ¬ surveillance-mirror ; consent-protected-rendering

  § STAGE-9 (cssl-render-v2::mise_en_abyme)
    @recursion_depth    : recursion-depth bounded by KAN-budget (≤ 4)
    @creature_eye       : creature-eye-Sovereign protections honored
    @no_spy_mirror      : ¬ cross-region-spy-mirror ; true-recursive-ray-cast
    @consent_protect    : witness-cells require Witness Φ-handle

  § STAGE-10 (cssl-render-v2 tonemap)
    @aces2_curve     : ACES-2 reference matches expected output
    @colorspace      : sRGB / DCI-P3 / Rec.2020 selectable
    @bloom_correct   : bloom passes match reference-impl

  § STAGE-11 (cssl-host-openxr AppSW)
    @motion_vec      : motion-vector accuracy ≥ 99% reference
    @depth_reproject : depth-reprojection error < 1px

  § STAGE-12 (cssl-host-openxr XR-compose)
    @cs_compose      : Compositor-Services frame-submit handshake
    @latency         : motion-to-photon < 18ms target

