§ HARDWARE-TARGET-ENVELOPE

  § DAY-ONE TARGETS (must-ship-on)
    Quest-3            : Snapdragon XR2 Gen 2, Adreno 740, 8GB LPDDR5X
                          target : 90Hz @ foveated-1080p, 11.1 ms / frame
                          ≡ canonical-reference-hardware @ S11
    Quest-3-Pro        : same chipset, more-RAM
                          target : same as Quest-3 (within margin)
    Vision Pro (R1+M2) : Apple-Silicon M2 + R1, 16GB unified
                          target : 90Hz @ 4K-eye, ~7 ms / frame
                          ≡ Compositor-Services bridge required
                          ≡ MSL backend (cssl-cgen-gpu-msl) primary

  § PC TIER-1 (recommended-spec)
    RTX-50 series      : DX12-Ultimate work-graph + CoopMatrix tier active
                          target : 144Hz @ 1440p, 6.9 ms / frame
                          ≡ rtx50_max config validates 0.71 ms Stage-6 budget
    Arc-A770+ / 9070   : Vulkan VK_NV_DGC fallback work-graph
                          target : 90Hz @ 1440p, 11.1 ms / frame

  § PC TIER-2 (minimum-spec)
    RTX-30 / RDNA2     : non-CoopMatrix tier ; SIMD-warp dispatch
                          target : 60Hz @ 1080p foveated, 16.6 ms / frame
                          ≡ Stage-6 falls-to SIMD-warp tier (2.51 ms)

  § HANDHELD / LOW-END (degraded-but-functional)
    Steam-Deck-class   : Vulkan, RDNA2-mobile, 90W TDP
                          target : 60Hz @ 720p, 16.6 ms / frame
                          ≡ Scalar tier (10.07 ms Stage-6) ; quality reduced
    Quest-2 (legacy)   : DEFERRED — Σ-render-budget too tight for 6-novelty-paths
                          may-degrade-novelty-paths (V.6 mise-en-abyme disabled)

  § 5-YEAR-FUTURE TARGETS (architectural-posture)
    Quest-4 / Vision-2 : assume 2× perf, 2× RAM, eye-tracker improved
                          target : 144Hz @ foveated-2K, full-novelty-paths
    RTX-60 / RDNA5     : assume CoopMatrix + work-graph mainstream
                          target : 240Hz @ 4K, headroom for V.5 + V.6 expanded
    AR-glasses         : DEFERRED — pass-through compositing requires
                          new ProjectionKind::ARPassThrough (§§ 30_v1 D-4)

  § CROSS-PLATFORM-BACKEND-MATRIX
    SPIR-V (Vulkan)    : cssl-cgen-gpu-spirv ; Quest, PC-Linux, PC-Windows-Vulkan
    DXIL (DX12)        : cssl-cgen-gpu-dxil ; PC-Windows-DX12
    MSL (Metal)        : cssl-cgen-gpu-msl ; Vision Pro + macOS
    WGSL (WebGPU)      : cssl-cgen-gpu-wgsl ; browser-fallback (DEFERRED prod)
    Level-Zero         : cssl-host-level-zero ; Intel-discrete (Arc / Battlemage)

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

§ NOVELTY-PATH × PIPELINE-STAGE COMPOSITION-MATRIX

  ```text
                  V.1   V.2   V.3   V.4   V.5   V.6
  Stage-1          ·     ·     ·     ·     ·     ·
  Stage-2          ·     ·     ·    ★      ·     ·
  Stage-3         ●     ·     ·     ·    ●     ·
  Stage-4        ★     ·     ·     ·     ●     ·
  Stage-5         ●     ·     ●     ·     ·     ·
  Stage-6         ·    ★     ·     ·     ·     ·
  Stage-7         ·     ●    ★     ·     ·     ·
  Stage-8         ·     ·     ·     ●     ●     ·
  Stage-9         ·     ·     ·     ·     ·    ★
  Stage-10        ·    ●     ·     ·     ·     ·
  Stage-11        ·     ·     ·     ·     ·     ·
  Stage-12        ·     ·     ·     ·     ·     ·
  ```
  ★ = primary-stage (novelty-path's home)
  ● = consumer / contributor

  composition-rule : every novelty-path has EXACTLY-ONE primary-stage ;
                     paths-cross via stable-API contracts above.

